data.description:
This home is bigger than it looks from the outside with over 2000 sqft of first floor living space! While entering through the covered front porch, you walk into the spacious mudroom with a slider to the back patio. To the right, you will find a custom built media room with  brilliant built in storage, electric fireplace and seating, Both this room and the main living are wired for speakers! This room could potentially be turned into a 3rd bedroom as well!
Both bedrooms are large! Primary bedroom is an ensuite connecting to the full bath w laundry, has 2 closets and sliding door offering natural light and access to the patio.
Buyers can rest easy knowing that the furnace and AC new in 2022 and roof in 2019! Conveniently located close to the highway, this home is an absolute must see!
